        "title": "Brief Outline",
        "content": "Theme: The humble soul’s total reliance on God’s mercy for guidance, forgiveness, and protection.\n\n1. The Upward Look of Trust (Verses 1 to 3)\n\n2. The Inward Request for Instruction (Verses 4 to 5)\n\n3. The Backward Plea for Forgiveness (Verses 6 to 11)\n\n4. The Outward Reward of the God-Fearing (Verses 12 to 15)\n\n5. The Downward Cry of the Distressed (Verses 16 to 21)\n\n6. The Forward Prayer for the Nation (Verse 22)"
