        "title": "Brief Outline",
        "content": "Theme: The Providential Vindication of the Patient Believer\n\n1. The Call to Quiet Trust (Verses 1 to 11)\n\nA command to stop fretting and start trusting God's timing.\n\n2. The Contrast of Destinies (Verses 12 to 22)\n\nA comparison between the plotting of the wicked and the provision of the Lord.\n\n3. The Security of the Righteous (Verses 23 to 31)\n\nThe assurance of God’s guidance and preservation throughout life.\n\n4. The Final Recompense (Verses 32 to 40)\n\nThe ultimate cutting off of the wicked and the salvation of the righteous."
