        "title": "Context Type",
        "content": "This chapter is classified as an Individual Lament and a Prayer for Vindication. It functions as a judicial appeal to the heavenly court. The psalmist shifts from the internal questioning of the previous chapter to an external petition for legal clearance and physical restoration to the Holy Hill."
