          "The Bottle of Tears: Conservative Christology sees in verse 8 a shadow of the High Priestly ministry of Jesus, who is touched by the feeling of our infirmities. The tears David shed are perfected in the strong crying and tears offered by Christ (Hebrews 5:7).",
