        "content": "Theme: A liturgical call to celebrate God's historical deliverance coupled with a prophetic lament over the tragedy of Israel's persistent disobedience.\n\nI. The Summons to National Celebration (Verses 1 to 3)\n\nII. The Legal Basis for the Festival (Verses 4 to 5)\n\nIII. The Divine Narrative of Deliverance and Testing (Verses 6 to 7)\n\nIV. The Covenant Mandate Against Idolatry (Verses 8 to 10)\n\nV. The Judicial Consequence of Stubbornness (Verses 11 to 12)\n\nVI. The Divine Yearning for Restoration and Provision (Verses 13 to 16)"
