          "The Serpent Crusher: Verse 13 predicts the treading upon the lion and the serpent, which is a messianic reference to the Seed of the woman crushing the head of the serpent as promised in Genesis 3:15.",
          "The Resurrection Promise: The closing promise of long life and showing him salvation finds its ultimate fulfillment in the resurrection and exaltation of Jesus Christ, who was delivered from the power of death and given a name above every name."
