        "title": "Brief Outline",
        "content": "Theme: The Eternal King Provides Stability and Hope for His Vanishing People.\n\nI. The Cry of the Perishing Individual (Verses 1-11)\n\nII. The Confidence in the Eternal King (Verses 12-17)\n\nIII. The Hope for Future Generations (Verses 18-22)\n\nIV. The Contrast between Human Frailty and Divine Immutability (Verses 23-28)"
