        "title": "Brief Outline",
        "content": "Theme: The Patient Gaze of the Afflicted Servant upon the Sovereign Lord.\n\nI. The Upward Look: Acknowledging the Sovereignty of the Heavenly King (Verse 1).\n\nII. The Attentive Posture: The Parable of the Servant’s Eyes (Verse 2).\n\nIII. The Earnest Petition: A Repeated Cry for Sovereign Mercy (Verse 3).\n\nIV. The Present Burden: Endurance Amidst the Mockery of the Arrogant (Verse 4)."
