        "title": "Brief Outline",
        "content": "Theme: The desperate appeal of the lonely believer to the all-knowing and all-sufficient God.\n\n1. The Outpouring of Personal Distress (Verses 1-2)\n\n2. The Recognition of Divine Omniscience (Verse 3a)\n\n3. The Reality of Human Abandonment (Verses 3b-4)\n\n4. The Declaration of Divine Sufficiency (Verse 5)\n\n5. The Final Plea for Deliverance and Praise (Verses 6-7)"
